Class ReplicationConfigurationDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.objects.ReplicationConfigurationDetails
All Implemented Interfaces:
DimensionsObjectDetails
Direct Known Subclasses:
BaselineReplicationConfigurationDetails, ItemReplicationConfigurationDetails, RequestReplicationConfigurationDetails
public abstract class ReplicationConfigurationDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements DimensionsObjectDetails

Represents the details of an abstract Dimensions replication configuration. This object cannot be instantiated directly, you must use one of its subclasses: ItemReplicationConfigurationDetails or BaselineReplicationConfigurationDetails.
